{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Headers.keys()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/keys","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers\"><code>Headers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/Headers\"><code>Headers()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><em><code>keys()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><code><strong>Headers.keys()&nbsp;</strong></code>方法返回一个 headers(Object) 对象所有 key 组成的迭代器，通过迭代器可以遍历 headers 这个对象，返回的迭代器中的元素&nbsp;key 都是字符串。</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>注意</strong>: 这个方法在&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>&nbsp;也可以使用。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">headers.keys();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回 <code>headers</code>&nbsp;对象中所有 key 组成的迭代器&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight:[7] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 创建一个 Headers 对象</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myHeaders <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Headers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyHeaders<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Content-Type'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'text/xml'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyHeaders<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Vary'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Accept-Language'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 显示 Headers 中所有的 key</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> key <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> myHeaders<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">keys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>控制台打印结果：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">content-type\nvary</pre>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容","isH3":false,"query":"api.Headers.keys","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/keys/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Service_Worker_API\">ServiceWorker API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS\">HTTP access control (CORS)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP\">HTTP</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>\n <audio class=\"hidden\"></audio>\n</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"返回 headers 对象中所有 key 组成的迭代器 iterator。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Headers.keys()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/headers/keys","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/headers/keys/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers","title":"Headers"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers/keys","title":"Headers.keys()"}],"pageTitle":"Headers.keys() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}